Conflicts:
 daemon-vca (<< 2.3.26+ubuntu22.04.6)
Replaces:
 daemon-vca (<< 2.3.26+ubuntu22.04.6)
Description: Intel VCA host userspace management tools
 This package provides vcactl, vcactld, udev rules, systemd service files,
 configuration files, and host-side scripts for Intel Visual Compute
 Accelerator cards.  It is based on Intel VCA 2.3.26 userspace with Python 3
 and Ubuntu 22.04 dependency updates.

Package: vca2-host
Architecture: all
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 vca2-vcass-modules-dkms,
 daemon-vca
Description: Intel VCA2 host stack metapackage
 This metapackage depends on the DKMS kernel module package and the userspace
 VCA management package.
